<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tokyo Travel Guide</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Tokyo Travel Guide</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="display-4">Discover Tokyo: A City of Vibrant Culture and Rich History</h1>
        <p class="lead">Tokyo, the capital city of Japan, is a fascinating metropolis that seamlessly blends traditional and modern culture. From ancient temples and shrines to cutting-edge technology and innovative cuisine, Tokyo has something to offer for every interest and taste.</p>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4 mt-5">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/Tokyo%20Skytree" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Tokyo Skytree">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Tokyo Skytree</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">At 634 meters tall, Tokyo Skytree is the tallest tower in the world, offering breathtaking views of the city from its observation decks. Visitors can enjoy shopping and dining at the tower's base, or take a lift to the top for a panoramic view of Tokyo.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/Shibuya%20Crossing" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Shibuya Crossing">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Shibuya Crossing</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">One of the busiest intersections in the world, Shibuya Crossing is a must-visit destination for people-watching and entertainment. The area is surrounded by trendy shops, cafes, and restaurants, and is especially famous for its unique and colorful street fashion.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/Meiji%20Shrine" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Meiji Shrine">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Meiji Shrine</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Dedicated to the deified spirits of Emperor Meiji and his wife, Empress Shoken, the Meiji Shrine is a serene Shinto shrine located in a tranquil forested area. Visitors can explore the shrine's grounds, which include beautiful gardens and a peaceful atmosphere.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src="https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/map%20of%20Tokyo%20style%20minimal" alt="Map of Tokyo" style="width:100%; border-radius:10px;" class="mt-5">
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>